Virtual Environments

.bashrc:
source $HOME/shf3.vre/bin/shfrc

Knife:
http://wiki.opscode.com/display/chef/Installing+Chef+Server+Manually

## Install Chef server on Ubuntu:
A$ install_chef_server
A$ install_chef_local_admin

## Create remote admin user
A$ vre create knife admin macbook

## Create your local knife-block
H$ mkdir knife
H$ cd knife
## Create and get the macbook knife from vadmin
H$ vre create knife vadmin/macbook
H$ vre login macbook
K$ knife client list

